headline: UBS Lowers Veralto (VLTO) PT to $102 with Neutral Rating
summary: Veralto Corporation (NYSE:VLTO) is one of the best IPO stocks to buy right now. On February 6, UBS analyst Joshua Spector lowered the firm’s price target for Veralto to $102 from $109 while keeping a Neutral rating on the shares.
